questionsAndAnswers.question: What is eCommerce website design and development?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: eCommerce website design and development is the process of creating an online store that allows businesses to sell their products or services over the internet. It involves designing an attractive, user-friendly interface, developing the website functionality (shopping cart, payment processing, etc.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Which eCommerce platforms do you work with?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
I work with popular eCommerce platforms including:

Shopify
WooCommerce (WordPress)
Magento
BigCommerce
Wix eCommerce
Squarespace

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my online store be mobile-friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! All eCommerce websites I design are fully responsive, meaning they will work flawlessly on smartphones, tablets, and desktops. This ensures a smooth shopping experience for your customers, no matter what device they use.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide SEO services for my online store?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: es, I offer SEO-optimized eCommerce websites. I integrate essential SEO elements, such as keyword optimization, meta tags, and alt text for images, to help your site rank better on search engines like Google and attract organic traffic.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you integrate payment gateways into my online store?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely! I can integrate secure payment gateways such as PayPal, Stripe, and other trusted options into your online store, allowing your customers to complete transactions easily and safely.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How long does it take to build my eCommerce website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The timeline for developing your online store depends on the complexity of the project and your requirements. Generally, it takes 1-4 weeks for a custom eCommerce website to be completed. I will provide a detailed timeline once we discuss your specific needs.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer ongoing maintenance and support after the website is live?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I offer ongoing support and website maintenance to ensure your store runs smoothly. I can assist with updates, troubleshooting, product management, and any other support needs you may have.
